Is a "JF4 distributor" another name for the dreaded 009 centrifugal only
distributor? If so they are notorious for flat spots. Try replacing it
with a new or good 2ndhand SVDA distributor.

>The carbs ran great on a 2L transporter motor, but not on this this.

Did you rejet them for the smaller engine? Have they been set up to
"lean, best idle" and balanced?

